BACKUP AND RECOVERY STRATEGY
================================================================================
Company: Ahmnest SecureTech Solution
Effective Date: [Date]
Version: 1.0
================================================================================

1. OBJECTIVES
================================================================================
- Ensure data availability and integrity
- Minimize downtime in event of data loss
- Meet Recovery Time Objective (RTO): 4 hours
- Meet Recovery Point Objective (RPO): 15 minutes

2. BACKUP SCHEDULE
================================================================================
| Data Type | Frequency | Retention | Method |
|-----------|-----------|-----------|--------|
| Databases | Every 4 Hours | 30 Days | Automated |
| File Servers | Daily | 90 Days | Automated |
| Email | Continuous | 365 Days | Cloud-native |
| User Data | Daily | 30 Days | Automated |
| System Configs | Daily | 60 Days | Automated |

3. BACKUP LOCATIONS
================================================================================
| Location | Purpose | Retention |
|----------|---------|-----------|
| On-Premise NAS | Fast recovery | 7 Days |
| Cloud (AWS) | Off-site retention | 90 Days |
| Offline (Tape) | Long-term archive | 7 Years |

4. RECOVERY PROCEDURES
================================================================================
| Scenario | RTO | Procedure |
|----------|-----|-----------|
| Single File Restore | 15 min | User self-service |
| Database Corruption | 2 hours | IT restore from backup |
| Server Failure | 4 hours | Bare metal restore |
| Site Disaster | 8 hours | Cloud failover |

5. TESTING
================================================================================
| Test Type | Frequency | Success Criteria |
|-----------|-----------|------------------|
| File Restore | Monthly | Successful restore |
| Database Restore | Quarterly | Successful restore |
| Full DR Test | Annually | RTO/RPO met |

================================================================================
